class.name: Queue
class.description: Stack class implements the [b]first-in, first-out (FIFO)[/b] policy.

method.name: dequeue
method.description: Removes the oldest value on queue. [b]Complexity:[/b] [i]O(1)[/i]

method.name: enqueue
method.description: Insert a new value on queue. [b]Complexity:[/b] [i]O(1)[/i]

method.name: get_size
method.description: Returns how much value are on the queue. [b]Complexity:[/b] [i]O(1)[/i]

method.name: is_empty
method.description: Returns [code]true[/code] if there are no values on the queue, and [code]false[/code] if there are values on the queue. [b]Complexity:[/b] [i]O(1)[/i]
